T1  - How do CEOs seek advice from CMOs vs. CTOs in radical innovation decision making under uncertainty?
AU  - Wilden, Ralf
AU  - Lin, Nidthida
AU  - Chirico, Francesco
AU  - Khan, Saad
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 54
IS  - 10
SP  - 105324
